Unarmed Strike with Piercer Feat - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Unarmed Strike&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes an Unarmed Strike*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}!cf<1cs>@{selected|unarmed_strike_die} [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Dexterity_mod} [Dex]]] [Dex] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Piercing damage.&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Piercing + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice and you must use the new roll. &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}cf<0cs>100]] Piercing&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
