Unarmed Strike-Piercer-Dex-Advantage
&{template:default} {{name=Melee - Unarmed Strike (Advantage)}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes an Unarmed Strike at **Advantage** *}} [[ [[ [[2d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}!!cf<1cs>@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Dexterity_mod} [Dex]]] [Dex] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Piercing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Piercing + $[[4]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** }} {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice and you must use the new roll. }} {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}cf<0cs>100]] Piercing}}
