&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Unarmed Strike&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes an Offhand Unarmed Strike attack at a target within range (Melee/20'/60').*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}!cf<1cs>@{selected|unarmed_strike_die} [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Piercing damage.&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[5]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Hit=Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals piercing damage you can reroll one of the attack's damage dice and you must use the new roll. &#125;&#125; {{Piercer Crit= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d@{selected|unarmed_strike_die}cf<0cs>100]] Piercing&#125;&#125;
